body: Yi, Your file is working for me: [](http://api.ning.com:80/files/ycvwLIslca7NoYmQhyrpnbBhwLTxPScAAEWm-IMML1cPc5PAvRtiK3HYl8tYGkQbP6mrJw6NfDfTo6DTxTf1UAzRNeem24Sl/CurvedSurfsWorking.JPG) Make sure that your rhino model is in meters and that your Rhino tolerance is small enough.  Then recompute the GH canvas and it should work. -Chris
